The Alex Jones Show
Friday, 29 July 2011


[sebaygo1]


Scheduled Guests
................

From the Infowars web site ::

Alex talks with frontman of the industrial metal band Ministry, Al Jourgensen, who was a frequent critic of the Bush administration and the invasion and occupation of Iraq. Jourgensen retired the band in 2008. 

Alex talks about the economy and other important issues with regular Friday guest, Bob Chapman, of the International Forecaster.

Today's broadcast ran 20 minutes into a 4th hour.
